<div class="description">
    <h3>Description</h3>

    <div class="body">
        <p>Add a way to link php errors to a Zend_Log object so that:</p>

<pre class="highlight"><code>
$log = Zend_Log::factory(...);
$log-&gt;registerErrorHandler();
</code></pre>

<p>would allow this to show up in the log:</p>

<pre class="highlight"><code>
trigger_error("Hello Notice", E_USER_NOTICE);
</code></pre>

